Package de.uni_potsdam.hpi.bpt.bp2014.jcomparser Description

This package contains the classes and subpackages of the JComparser. The JComaparser is a component responsible for retrieving models from the JEDItor Server to parse them and to write the information to a database for late useage inside the JEngine.
